text: Spitak (), is a town in the northern Lori Province of Armenia. Spitak may also refer to: *, a former administrative district around Spitak (1937—1995) *Spitak Pass, Armenia *Spitak River, a tributary of Chknakh in Debed river basin *Spitak earthquake *Spitak (film), a 2018 Armenian film
